descriptionList: Promising junior web developer and highly motivated person who has a huge will to learn, therefore development opportunities and challenging projects are prioritized. I am naturally motivated and driven to deliver objectives in a way that supports an outstanding customer experience for all of our clients.

I am a very focused and energetic person with strong external and internal relationship management skills allowing me to communicate effectively with people at all levels. I am ambitious and eager to acquire new skills and gain on the job experiences within a large organisation.
